                  "timeStart": "7.920",
                  "timeEnd": "9.840"
                },
                {
                  "text": "Philipp Schrangl , Mag.",
                  "timeStart": "9.840",
                  "timeEnd": "10.240"
                },
                {
                  "text": "Harald Stefan , Mag.",
